http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/karnataka/CSIR-Director-General-responds/article13993302.ece

Director-General of CSIR Girish Sahni said the CFTRI imbroglio had been referred to the Joint Secretary in-charge of Administration in the Union Ministry of Science and Technology.Speaking to The Hindu over phone, Dr. Sahni said he had acknowledged the receipt of the letter by Pratap Simha, MP, by giving an administrative response. “I assure you, we will do the needful,” Dr. Sahni said in his response. “But, I have no pre-conceived notions about the matter and the senior official from the Ministry will look into it,” he added.